dct_title_s: Geologic map of the Camatta Canyon quadrangle, San Luis Obispo County, California
dct_description_sm: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr. ; edited by John A. Minch.
Relief shown by contours and spot heights.
"Topographic base map from available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangle Camatta Canyon CA 1961. Revised 1993. DMA 1955 III SE - Series V895."
Includes quadrangle location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, and index to sources of geology.
